name: Himiko
skill: Deals 1773/2113 DMG to the 3 enemies with the highest ATK. A very high/100% chance of inflicting Silence.
ability: Moderately increases damage dealt by Divina team members when this daemon is Team Leader.

additional_data.description: The spirit of a shaman queen who ruled Yamataikoku long ago. Her shamanic powers were strong and she used them to save her domain many times. That's how she went from being one of may shrine maidens to being the queen. She actually enjoyed being a shrine maiden, but her serious side wouldn't permit her to turn down the offer to rule the land, so she's trying to start acting more like a queen. She unexpectedly finds it very fulfilling and is completely satisfied with her own role.

main: "Calm yourself! Who do you think you're talking to? (Yeah, that sounded queenly! Go me!)"
summon: "Worry not, I'll prevent anything bad from happening. (Ooh, did that really sound regal enough?)"
